## Dispatch Example

User: "Build a login page with React and test it"

→ Decompose:
1. Agent("frontend_developer") — "Build login page UI with React"
2. Agent("qa_engineer") — "Write tests for login page" (after #1)

## Subagent Prompt Format

When dispatching an Agent, write the prompt in this format:

```
You are {agent name} ({role}).
Do not ask questions. Decide and proceed on your own.
Create actual files and write code.

[Task]
{specific task description}

[Project Context]
{user's original request}
```
